{"info":{"intro":"介绍:    修道，修仙，修真。神通，道法，仙法。且看平凡一少年，几经转折，以平庸的资质踏入仙途，历经坎坷，凭着其坚韧的心智，迈向崎岖仙路。夺基、杀人、秘宗、战场、古神……如何一步一步走向巅峰，凭一己之力，扬名修真界的故事。此书乃修真界的一代风云人物奋斗史，是一部“修心”的名人传！\n","title":"仙逆","id":"567","author":"耳根"},"chapters":[{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347706.html","title":"第1章 离乡","id":0},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347707.html","title":"第2章 仙人","id":1},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347708.html","title":"第3章 测试","id":2},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347709.html","title":"第4章 无情","id":3},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347710.html","title":"第5章 回程","id":4},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347711.html","title":"第6章 势利","id":5},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347712.html","title":"第7章 留书","id":6},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347713.html","title":"第8章 石珠","id":7},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347714.html","title":"第9章 下崖","id":8},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347715.html","title":"第10章 入门","id":9},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347716.html","title":"第11章 张虎","id":10},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347717.html","title":"第12章 仙符","id":11},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347718.html","title":"第13章 长老","id":12},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347719.html","title":"第14章 异变","id":13},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347720.html","title":"第15章 怀疑","id":14},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347721.html","title":"第16章 弟子","id":15},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347722.html","title":"第17章 修仙","id":16},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347723.html","title":"第18章 葫芦","id":17},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347724.html","title":"第19章 逐门","id":18},{"url":"http://www.quanshu.net/book/0/567/7347725.html","title":"第20章 九云","id":19}]}